            <i>✦</i>
            <span>BOLD FOOD</span>
            <i>✦</i>
            <span>ALTERNATIVE SOUND</span>
            <i>✦</i>
            <span>LATE NIGHTS</span>
            <i>✦</i>
            <span>NO BORING TABLES</span>
            <i>✦</i>
            <span>RARE BEER</span>
            <i>✦</i>
            <span>BOLD FOOD</span>
