                <div class="rr-section-number">
                    01 / THE MOOD
                </div>

                <h2>
                    More than a pub.
                    <span>A controlled riot.</span>
                </h2>

                <p class="rr-manifesto-lead">
                    Rebel Rebel is built for people who want something
